Introduction

Sungkook, formerly known as Ahxian, is a South Korean singer and lyricist under KLAP Entertainment. He is a member of the boy group VANNER.

On March 22, 2024, it was announced that Sungkook will be enlisting on May 7 as an active duty soldier.
